Follow these coding guidelines:

- Always prefer simple solutions
- Avoid duplication of code whenever possible
- Check other areas of the codebase for similar code and functionality
- Keep the codebase very clean and organized
- Avoid having files over 200 lines of code
- Write documentation and tests for all major functionality
